### Trước Task 08
- [ ] `mekong-cli` repo ở `/Users/mac/mekong-cli/FnB-Container-Caffe`
- [ ] `wrangler` CLI installed + authenticated
- [ ] Backup D1: `npx wrangler d1 export fnb_caffe_db --output=backup-pre-v2.sql`

### Trước Task 11 (Thẻ giấy + POS)
