## 🆘 Rollback plans

### Task 08 (DB schema)
```bash
npx wrangler d1 execute fnb_caffe_db --remote --file=backup-pre-v2.sql
```

### Task 09/10/11 (Code)
```bash
git revert <merge-commit-sha>
git push origin main
cd worker && npx wrangler deploy
```

### Campaign disable tạm
```sql
UPDATE bonus_campaigns SET active = 0 WHERE code = 'GRAND_OPENING_28_5_2026';
```

